Manage validators (register, set gas price, commission)

Usage: soma validator [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  start                Start a validator node from a config file
  make-validator-info  Generate validator key files and info
  join-committee       Request to join the validator committee
  leave-committee      Request to leave the validator committee
  list                 List all active and pending validators
  display-metadata     Display validator metadata
  update-metadata      Update validator metadata
  set-commission-rate  Set commission rate for the next epoch
  report-validator     Report or un-report a validator
  report-model         Report or un-report a model (validators only)
  help                 Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --client.config <CONFIG>  Sets the file storing the state of our user accounts (an empty one will be created if missing)
      --client.env <ENV>        The Soma environment to use. This must be present in the current config file
  -y, --yes                     Create a new soma config without prompting if none exists
      --json                    Output as JSON
  -h, --help                    Print help

EXAMPLES:
    soma validator display-metadata
    soma validator list
